{"tid":1626303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"招聘啟事：傳道人！每個人都可以做嘅兼職","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T12:21:15.000Z","uid":262507,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4a4a434eec0eb924d64808c7dbb48faf3b9c20","tid":1626303,"uid":262507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:38:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不論你本身職業係和理非定蔥蔥子，你都可以做埋呢份兼職:</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />傳道人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">彈性開工時間/地點，非常缺人！</span><br />\n<br />\n事源我今日同朋友去茶餐廳食野，收到tg不同group都有人話ATM大排長龍，有個別銀行仲限制取款！<br />\n<br />\n咁既消息我當然即刻同我既朋友講：<span style=\"color: orange;\">哇我岩岩有個frd話出面既ATM機超多人排隊，仲限每人拎4000蚊，會唔會擠提架</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪我講野習慣大聲，周圍好多中年人都聽到我講野，佢地有d人都即場同自己既朋友討論。我即刻叮一聲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係喎，藍絲/老人家唔會睇連儂，消息都唔靈通，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">餐廳聽到既野係佢地其中一個主要信息來源！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以後有咩想spread開去，只要夠多人做傳道人，就會做到文宣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好處：</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n-突破同溫層<br />\n-唔洗透漏自己立場<br />\n-完全合法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-0成本</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做法：</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n-有朋友同你一齊，就同朋友講你想講既內容，<span style=\"color: gold;\">聲線唔洗特別大，更可以扮細細聲講</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-無朋友一齊就<span style=\"color: purple;\">扮傾電話/用WhatsApp錄音</span>功能<br />\n<br />\n-不限於餐廳，<span style=\"color: gold;\">搭巴士小巴或者等車都得，隨時隨地開工！</span><br />\n<br />\n-講d咩講幾多自己決定，但<span style=\"color: purple;\">建議一分鐘內</span>、同埋分幾次講，否則太假</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">-<span style=\"color: gold;\">建議講真野、生活化d、唔好屌9任何一邊，要講對淺黃中立藍絲有直接影響既野，要稱狗做警察、稱黨鐵為港鐵</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">例子：</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">-<strong>惡法有咩影響</strong>：股市會冧、外資會走、影響旅遊業<span style=\"color: gold;\">打爛好多人飯碗！</span><br />\n<br />\n-<strong>國際睇法：</strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">馬來西亞總理建議林鄭辭職、新加坡向香港發旅遊警示！</span>全球都唔睇好緊急法<br />\n<br />\n-<strong>生活化：</strong>港鐵年年加價！又唔開站服務市民，<span style=\"color: gold;\">只為警察服務</span>，721、831港鐵無做過野保護市民！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">-仲有大把可以自由發揮！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一齊叫朋友加入傳道人行列啦！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122a0ef9693a4d3c0f1cbc651fa6ee508b323650","tid":1626303,"uid":262507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:45:13.000Z","msg":"幫下p牌推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"efc385b19c982eacffcfaefb88371072701140aa","tid":1626303,"uid":262507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"2/10<br />\n呢行長期缺人"},{"pid":"c76e891fc53819a785a112cc606aac72860ae5cc","tid":1626303,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:53:55.000Z","msg":"【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"},{"pid":"883eba7d12395f71c52c1aee8449fcba1422d8d2","tid":1626303,"uid":262507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:02:35.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"680cc24b310740daafb559c348ebb6d368a15b1c","tid":1626303,"uid":330885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:03:06.000Z","msg":"應徵全職傳道人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26671f30235209125625bff03aa65b3f0dcdb2f","tid":1626303,"uid":262507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:15:43.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"d47554714ed5247408abc45a76bb6b4c09561d76","tid":1626303,"uid":262507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:25:02.000Z","msg":"5/10"},